{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.1","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:1","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.001.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Cantique d\u2019Anne. Samuel au service de l\u2019\u00c9ternel<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-11: cf. Lu 1:46-55.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Anne pria, et dit:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Mon c\u0153ur se r\u00e9jouit en l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ma force a \u00e9t\u00e9 relev\u00e9e par l\u2019\u00c9ternel;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ma bouche s\u2019est ouverte contre mes ennemis,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car je me r\u00e9jouis de ton secours.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.2","name":"1 Samuel 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.1.28","name":"1 Samuel 1:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.1.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.2","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:2","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Nul n\u2019est saint comme l\u2019\u00c9ternel;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Il n\u2019y a point d\u2019autre Dieu que toi;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il n\u2019y a point de rocher comme notre Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.3","name":"1 Samuel 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.1","name":"1 Samuel 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.3","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:3","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Ne parlez plus avec tant de hauteur;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Que l\u2019arrogance ne sorte plus de votre bouche;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car l\u2019\u00c9ternel est un Dieu qui sait tout,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et par lui sont pes\u00e9es toutes les actions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.4","name":"1 Samuel 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.2","name":"1 Samuel 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.4","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:4","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>L\u2019arc des puissants est bris\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et les faibles ont la force pour ceinture.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.5","name":"1 Samuel 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.3","name":"1 Samuel 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.5","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:5","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>\n    Ceux qui \u00e9taient rassasi\u00e9s se louent pour du pain,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ceux qui \u00e9taient affam\u00e9s se reposent;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">M\u00eame la st\u00e9rile enfante sept fois,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et celle qui avait beaucoup d\u2019enfants est fl\u00e9trie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.6","name":"1 Samuel 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.4","name":"1 Samuel 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.6","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:6","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>\n    L\u2019\u00c9ternel fait mourir et il fait vivre.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il fait descendre au s\u00e9jour des morts et il en fait remonter.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.7","name":"1 Samuel 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.5","name":"1 Samuel 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.7","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:7","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel appauvrit et il enrichit,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il abaisse et il \u00e9l\u00e8ve.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.8","name":"1 Samuel 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.6","name":"1 Samuel 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.8","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:8","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>\n    De la poussi\u00e8re il retire le pauvre,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Du fumier il rel\u00e8ve l\u2019indigent,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Pour les faire asseoir avec les grands.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et il leur donne en partage un tr\u00f4ne de gloire;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Car \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel sont les colonnes de la terre,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et c\u2019est sur elles qu\u2019il a pos\u00e9 le monde.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.9","name":"1 Samuel 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.7","name":"1 Samuel 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.9","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:9","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Il gardera les pas de ses bien-aim\u00e9s.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais les m\u00e9chants seront an\u00e9antis dans les t\u00e9n\u00e8bres;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car l\u2019homme ne triomphera point par la force.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.10","name":"1 Samuel 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.8","name":"1 Samuel 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.10","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:10","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Les ennemis de l\u2019\u00c9ternel trembleront;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Du haut des cieux il lancera sur eux son tonnerre;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">L\u2019\u00c9ternel jugera les extr\u00e9mit\u00e9s de la terre.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Il donnera la puissance \u00e0 son roi,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et il rel\u00e8vera la force de son oint.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.11","name":"1 Samuel 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.9","name":"1 Samuel 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.11","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:11","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Elkana s\u2019en alla dans sa maison \u00e0 Rama, et l\u2019enfant fut au service de l\u2019\u00c9ternel devant le sacrificateur \u00c9li.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.12","name":"1 Samuel 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.10","name":"1 Samuel 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.12","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:12","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.013,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Conduite coupable des fils d\u2019\u00c9li, et faiblesse de leur p\u00e8re<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 12-17: cf. (Os 4:6-10. Mal 2:1-9.) J\u00e9 7:3-11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Les fils d\u2019\u00c9li \u00e9taient des hommes pervers, ils ne connaissaient point l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.13","name":"1 Samuel 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.11","name":"1 Samuel 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.13","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:13","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Et voici quelle \u00e9tait la mani\u00e8re d\u2019agir de ces sacrificateurs \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard du peuple. Lorsque quelqu\u2019un offrait un sacrifice, le serviteur du sacrificateur arrivait au moment o\u00f9 l\u2019on faisait cuire la chair. Tenant \u00e0 la main une fourchette \u00e0 trois dents,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.14","name":"1 Samuel 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.12","name":"1 Samuel 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.14","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:14","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>il piquait dans la chaudi\u00e8re, dans le chaudron, dans la marmite, ou dans le pot; et tout ce que la fourchette amenait, le sacrificateur le prenait pour lui. C\u2019est ainsi qu\u2019ils agissaient \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard de tous ceux d\u2019Isra\u00ebl qui venaient l\u00e0 \u00e0 Silo.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.15","name":"1 Samuel 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.13","name":"1 Samuel 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.15","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:15","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>M\u00eame avant qu\u2019on f\u00eet br\u00fbler la graisse, le serviteur du sacrificateur arrivait et disait \u00e0 celui qui offrait le sacrifice: Donne pour le sacrificateur de la chair \u00e0 r\u00f4tir; il ne recevra de toi point de chair cuite, c\u2019est de la chair crue qu\u2019il veut.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.16","name":"1 Samuel 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.14","name":"1 Samuel 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.16","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:16","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Et si l\u2019homme lui disait: Quand on aura br\u00fbl\u00e9 la graisse, tu prendras ce qui te plaira, le serviteur r\u00e9pondait: Non! Tu donneras maintenant, sinon je prends de force.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.17","name":"1 Samuel 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.15","name":"1 Samuel 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.17","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:17","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Ces jeunes gens se rendaient coupables devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel d\u2019un tr\u00e8s grand p\u00e9ch\u00e9, parce qu\u2019ils m\u00e9prisaient les offrandes de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.18","name":"1 Samuel 2:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.16","name":"1 Samuel 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.18","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:18","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.019,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 18-21: cf. 1 S 1:20-28. Ps 128.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Samuel faisait le service devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et cet enfant \u00e9tait rev\u00eatu d\u2019un \u00e9phod de lin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.19","name":"1 Samuel 2:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.17","name":"1 Samuel 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.19","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:19","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Sa m\u00e8re lui faisait chaque ann\u00e9e une petite robe, et la lui apportait en montant avec son mari pour offrir le sacrifice annuel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.20","name":"1 Samuel 2:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.18","name":"1 Samuel 2:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.20","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:20","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>\u00c9li b\u00e9nit Elkana et sa femme, en disant: Que l\u2019\u00c9ternel te fasse avoir des enfants de cette femme, pour remplacer celui qu\u2019elle a pr\u00eat\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel! Et ils s\u2019en retourn\u00e8rent chez eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.21","name":"1 Samuel 2:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.19","name":"1 Samuel 2:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.21","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:21","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Lorsque l\u2019\u00c9ternel eut visit\u00e9 Anne, elle devint enceinte, et elle enfanta trois fils et deux filles. Et le jeune Samuel grandissait aupr\u00e8s de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.22","name":"1 Samuel 2:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.20","name":"1 Samuel 2:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.22","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:22","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.023,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 22-26: cf. De 21:18-21. Pr 15:10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>\u00c9li \u00e9tait fort \u00e2g\u00e9 et il apprit comment ses fils agissaient \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard de tout Isra\u00ebl; il apprit aussi qu\u2019ils couchaient avec les femmes qui s\u2019assemblaient \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e de la tente d\u2019assignation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.23","name":"1 Samuel 2:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.21","name":"1 Samuel 2:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.23","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:23","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Il leur dit: Pourquoi faites-vous de telles choses? Car j\u2019apprends de tout le peuple vos mauvaises actions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.24","name":"1 Samuel 2:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.22","name":"1 Samuel 2:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.24","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:24","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Non, mes enfants, ce que j\u2019entends dire n\u2019est pas bon; vous faites p\u00e9cher le peuple de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.25","name":"1 Samuel 2:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.23","name":"1 Samuel 2:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.25","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:25","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Si un homme p\u00e8che contre un autre homme, Dieu le jugera; mais s\u2019il p\u00e8che contre l\u2019\u00c9ternel, qui interc\u00e9dera pour lui? Et ils n\u2019\u00e9cout\u00e8rent point la voix de leur p\u00e8re, car l\u2019\u00c9ternel voulait les faire mourir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.26","name":"1 Samuel 2:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.24","name":"1 Samuel 2:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.26","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:26","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Le jeune Samuel continuait \u00e0 grandir, et il \u00e9tait agr\u00e9able \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel et aux hommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.27","name":"1 Samuel 2:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.25","name":"1 Samuel 2:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.27","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:27","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.028,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Sentence de l\u2019\u00c9ternel contre la maison d\u2019\u00c9li<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 27-36: cf. 1 S 3:11-14. (1 S 4:11-18; 22:16-21. 1 R 2:26, 27, 35. \u00c9z 44:15, 16.) Os 8:7.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Un homme de Dieu vint aupr\u00e8s d\u2019\u00c9li, et lui dit: Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Ne me suis-je pas r\u00e9v\u00e9l\u00e9 \u00e0 la maison de ton p\u00e8re, lorsqu\u2019ils \u00e9taient en \u00c9gypte dans la maison de Pharaon?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.28","name":"1 Samuel 2:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.26","name":"1 Samuel 2:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.28","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:28","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Je l\u2019ai choisie parmi toutes les tribus d\u2019Isra\u00ebl pour \u00eatre \u00e0 mon service dans le sacerdoce, pour monter \u00e0 mon autel, pour br\u00fbler le parfum, pour porter l\u2019\u00e9phod devant moi, et j\u2019ai donn\u00e9 \u00e0 la maison de ton p\u00e8re tous les sacrifices consum\u00e9s par le feu et offerts par les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.29","name":"1 Samuel 2:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.27","name":"1 Samuel 2:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.29","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:29","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Pourquoi foulez-vous aux pieds mes sacrifices et mes offrandes, que j\u2019ai ordonn\u00e9 de faire dans ma demeure? Et d\u2019o\u00f9 vient que tu honores tes fils plus que moi, afin de vous engraisser des pr\u00e9mices de toutes les offrandes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, mon peuple?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.30","name":"1 Samuel 2:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.28","name":"1 Samuel 2:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.30","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:30","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi voici ce que dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: J\u2019avais d\u00e9clar\u00e9 que ta maison et la maison de ton p\u00e8re marcheraient devant moi \u00e0 perp\u00e9tuit\u00e9. Et maintenant, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, loin de moi! Car j\u2019honorerai celui qui m\u2019honore, mais ceux qui me m\u00e9prisent seront m\u00e9pris\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.31","name":"1 Samuel 2:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.29","name":"1 Samuel 2:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.31","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:31","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Voici, le temps arrive o\u00f9 je retrancherai ton bras et le bras de la maison de ton p\u00e8re, en sorte qu\u2019il n\u2019y aura plus de vieillard dans ta maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.32","name":"1 Samuel 2:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.30","name":"1 Samuel 2:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.32","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:32","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Tu verras un adversaire dans ma demeure, tandis qu\u2019Isra\u00ebl sera combl\u00e9 de biens par l\u2019\u00c9ternel; et il n\u2019y aura plus jamais de vieillard dans ta maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.33","name":"1 Samuel 2:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.31","name":"1 Samuel 2:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.33","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:33","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Je laisserai subsister aupr\u00e8s de mon autel l\u2019un des tiens, afin de consumer tes yeux et d\u2019attrister ton \u00e2me; mais tous ceux de ta maison mourront dans la force de l\u2019\u00e2ge.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.34","name":"1 Samuel 2:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.32","name":"1 Samuel 2:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.34","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:34","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Et tu auras pour signe ce qui arrivera \u00e0 tes deux fils, Hophni et Phin\u00e9es; ils mourront tous les deux le m\u00eame jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.35","name":"1 Samuel 2:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.33","name":"1 Samuel 2:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.35","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:35","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.002.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Je m\u2019\u00e9tablirai un sacrificateur fid\u00e8le, qui agira selon mon c\u0153ur et selon mon \u00e2me; je lui b\u00e2tirai une maison stable, et il marchera toujours devant mon oint.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.36","name":"1 Samuel 2:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.34","name":"1 Samuel 2:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.36","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 2:36","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.002.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.003.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.2.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Et quiconque restera de ta maison viendra se prosterner devant lui pour avoir une pi\u00e8ce d\u2019argent et un morceau de pain, et dira: Attache-moi, je te prie, \u00e0 l\u2019une des fonctions du sacerdoce, afin que j\u2019aie un morceau de pain \u00e0 manger.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2","name":"1 Samuel 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.3.1","name":"1 Samuel 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.3.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.2.35","name":"1 Samuel 2:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.2.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb23f3144.76362341');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb23f3144.76362341\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb23f3144.76362341","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb23f3144.76362341'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb23f3144.76362341\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}